-- U.S. likely to post new offshore drilling ban Monday
-- 
-- Mon Jul 12, 2010 3:57pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/07/12/us-oil-spill-moratorium-idUSTRE66B4L420100712

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - The Obama administration is likely to announce revised rules banning deepwater offshore drilling on Monday, an administration official said. 

 The announcement was expected after an original blanket ban was struck down by a federal court. (Reporting by  Jeff Mason , Editing by Sandra Maler)